    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm already on the first coat but i'm worried about the corners especially. sometimes it feels like there's some weird debris or stuff stuck in the gaps before i even get the tape on. how do i make sure the seam is totally clean before i start mucking it up?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
