      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay got it. i've been using a vacuum but i still keep finding these tiny little bits of stuff deep in the cracks that i can't seem to reach. it's kind of annoying. is there a specific tool or something i should use to clear out those deeper spots so nothing ruins the finish later?",
